item.title: Barrelmanboy-Treason [Project, WIP, Remixable, Collab?]
item.dc:creator: Barrelmanboy
item.description:
I like how you made the sounds sound unique, and I enjoy how you used the first part of the song as your main focus. However, from what I have experienced, I was really hoping you would have used the second part of the song as your main focus. I could almost hear the remix already, with that specific tune. If you would, it’d be nice if I got the second part of my song remixed. I hope it’s not too much, but I also hope you understand!
